266
00:15:45,189 --> 00:15:46,626
Could mean 100 grand.

267
00:15:58,505 --> 00:16:01,647
This takes longer than 30 seconds,
you're in the canal.

268
00:16:03,168 --> 00:16:04,178
Bait...

269
00:16:04,333 --> 00:16:05,376
for the catfish.

270
00:16:18,495 --> 00:16:20,265
You just gave me a 100,000 reasons

271
00:16:20,684 --> 00:16:22,706
- to turn you in.
