00:35:59,957 --> 00:36:02,614
He hasn't shot anybody,
he hasn't hurt anybody, please! Michael!

526
00:36:03,266 --> 00:36:04,634
Michael, tell them the truth!

527
00:36:05,914 --> 00:36:07,719
He's done nothing wrong!

528
00:36:35,799 --> 00:36:36,819
Hey, it's me.

529
00:36:37,796 --> 00:36:39,017
Getting impatient.

530
00:36:39,833 --> 00:36:41,621
Reminds me of when we were in college.

531
00:36:43,465 --> 00:36:44,800
Did you buy the tickets yet?

532
00:36:45,531 --> 00:36:47,152
<i>No, I'm still looking.</i>

533
00:36:48,251 --> 00:36:49,301
Don't.

534
00:36:50,601 --> 00:36:51,604
What?

535
00:36:52,021 --> 00:36:53,595
Forget about them.

536
00:36:56,888 --> 00:36:58,308
Forget I ever existed.

537
00:37:22,983 --> 00:37:24,002
Excuse me.

538
00:37:24,218 --> 00:37:25,170
Do you speak English?

539
00:37:25,171 --> 00:37:26,466
- Yes, can I help you?
- Yeah.

540
00:37:26,483 --> 00:37:27,870
I'm looking for a woman, Sarah Tancredi.

541
00:37:27,945 --> 00:37:31,607
She was brought in to give her statement
and then released. You just missed her.

542
00:38:19,422 --> 00:38:21,094
I thought you'd never show up.

543
00:38:26,051 --> 00:38:27,634
When am I getting out of here?

544
00:38:28,349 --> 00:38:29,419
That's the thing.

545
00:38:29,897 --> 00:38:31,385
There's been a hiccup.

546
00:38:32,698 --> 00:38:34,153
A hiccup...

547
00:38:34,988 --> 00:38:36,275
Look, you got me...

548
00:38:36,743 --> 00:38:39,033
You got me fair and square
in Mexico, alright.

549
00:38:39,676 --> 00:38:41,334
I did what you wanted me to do.

550
00:38:41,398 --> 00:38:43,487
Now it's time to cut me loose
just like we agreed.

551
00:38:43,488 --> 00:38:45,393
Getting caught wasn't part
of the agreement.

552
00:38:45,394 --> 00:38:47,665
I got caught running your setup,

553
00:38:48,150 --> 00:38:49,604
being your bait.

554
00:38:50,223 --> 00:38:53,036
Now I got you Scofield down here.
I got you what you wanted!

555
00:38:55,501 --> 00:38:57,620
You got caught, Bagwell.

556
00:38:59,793 --> 00:39:00,879
Where you going?

557
00:39:03,787 --> 00:39:07,867
I got you what you want!
I got them boys down here!

558
00:39:07,933 --> 00:39:10,085
I did what you told me to do!

559
00:39:11,467 --> 00:39:12,536
Do you hear me?

560
00:39:12,569 --> 00:39:14,625
I did what you told me to do!

561
00:39:15,681 --> 00:39:17,085
I did what you told me!

562
00:40:28,162 --> 00:40:29,666
This is as far as I go.

563
00:40:55,564 --> 00:40:56,566
General...

564
00:41:00,046 --> 00:41:02,118
I trust this is a safe place to speak.

565
00:41:03,547 --> 00:41:04,634
It's Scofield.

566
00:41:05,763 --> 00:41:06,849
They got him.

567
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:48,478
Scofield back in the penn.

568
00:41:48,648 --> 00:41:51,768
Got to be honest, we didn't think
we'd see it happen.

569
00:41:54,200 --> 00:41:55,768
You know he's gonna break out.

570
00:41:56,353 --> 00:41:57,707
It's in his blood.

571
00:41:59,529 --> 00:42:01,568
That's exactly what we want him to do.

